hree-point head shots in the early stages, but Cunningham ducked and spun and fired into the body for two points himself, to take the first round.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999987852418701, \"rank\": 1.2147590061664464e-06, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Salimi\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"his long legs\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"three-point head shots\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"the early stages\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"two points\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second round was cagey as Salimi chose his moments more carefully, and this time his toe extended out and clipped Cunningham's head guard to force a decider.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999987852418701, \"rank\": 1.2147590061664464e-06, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second round\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"cagey\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"Salimi\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"his moments\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"his toe\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"a decider\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There, two more head kicks proved decisive for gold.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two more head kicks\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite defeat, Cunningham lapped up the moment, playing to the crowd and relishing the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999987852418701, \"rank\": 1.2147590061664464e-06, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud of myself,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Gutted, but I am proud nevertheless.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Gutted\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done a good job today, took out some big people.\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good job\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"some big people\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That fighter was amazing, he was better than me today, so that's on me.\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That fighter\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will work to make it better so there is none of this silver going on.\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"this silver\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My opponent was the same as me: when we are in the ring we are ready to kill; outside, respect.\\\"\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My opponent\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cunningham took up the sport aged six, inheriting his father's love of martial arts, and he was soon mapping out his Olympic future.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3195, \"end\": 3205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999987852418701, \"rank\": 1.2147590061664464e-06, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"his father's love\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"martial arts\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic future\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would take on fights against bigger, stronger boys who would leave him feeling \\\"beaten up\\\", but he enjoyed the challenge of learning the techniques to overcome the physical deficit.\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fights\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger, stronger boys\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"the techniques\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"the physical deficit\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He suffered a major setback in his first fight of the 2022 World Championships when he felt the anterior cruciate ligament snap in his knee.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major setback\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"his first fight\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 World Championships\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"the anterior cruciate ligament\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"his knee\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Cunningham's attitude was to harness the adversity.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999987852418701, \"rank\": 1.2147590061664464e-06, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the adversity\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just thought, this is going to make it a cooler story when I do go [to the Olympics].\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really knuckled down.\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw it as an opportunity to grow and come back an absolute monster.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolute monster\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what I did.\\\"\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The future could be anything for Cunningham now.\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3952, \"end\": 3962, \"titl